will also each receive five of J. Edgar Hoover's chiffon dresses, three of his 
silk blouses and a pair of matching pumps." 
</P>
<P>
 Peyser, on a Redbook survey claiming that women think sex is over-rated, that 
29% would rather relax on the beach and that 28% would prefer a romantic 
dinner: "That's fine with most men -- as long as they can have sex first." 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
