<P>
 When reader Harriet Knight of Valencia tucked her 9-year-old son in bed the 
other night, he told her that he felt nauseated. She immediately went into a 
tirade about how he had overdone it while playing with the dog after a recent 
bout with flu. 
</P>
<P>
 "No, Mom, it's not the flu," he replied. "I was just reading that book about 
sex you got for me."  
</P>
