<P>
ISRAEL ALLEGEDLY STAGES MOCK RAIDS OVER LEBANON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Israeli warplanes staged mock air raids against radical Palestinian bases 
south of Beirut on Tuesday, security sources said. 
</P>
<P>
 The planes crisscrossed at low altitude over Naame, nine miles south of 
Beirut. Antiaircraft machine guns were fired, but the planes were not hit, the 
sources said. 
</P>
